OL,6,FHarvey Weinstein is serving a lengthy
OL,7,Fjail sentence for other sex crimes,
OL,8,Fbut will now face a retrial, as ITV
OL,9,FNews Correspondent Robert Moore reports
OL,11,FNew York's highest court overturned
OL,12,FHarvey Weinstein's 2020 rape
OL,13,Fconviction on Thursday.
OL,15,FIt found the judge at the landmark
OL,16,F_MeToo trial prejudiced the ex-movie
OL,17,Fmogul with "egregious" improper
OL,18,Frulings.
