OL,6,FActress Ashley Judd, who was among the
OL,7,Ffirst women to make allegations on the
OL,8,Frecord against Weinstein, said the
OL,9,Fcourt's decision was "unfair to
OL,10,Fsurvivors".
OL,12,F"We conclude that the trial court
OL,13,Ferroneously admitted testimony of
OL,14,Funcharged, alleged prior sexual acts
OL,15,Fagainst persons other than the
OL,16,Fcomplainants of the underlying
OL,17,Fcrimes," the court's 4-3 decision said.
OL,19,F"The remedy for these egregious errors
OL,20,Fis a new trial."
