OL,6,FOne of the key issues the court found
OL,7,Fwas a decision to let women testify
OL,8,Fabout allegations that were not part
OL,9,Fof the case.
OL,11,FThe state Court of Appeals ruling re-
OL,12,Fopens a chapter in America with sexual
OL,13,Fmisconduct allegations against
OL,14,Fpowerful figures being exposed.
OL,16,FThe _MeToo era began to gain
OL,17,Fwidespread momentum in 2017, with a
OL,18,Fflood of allegations against Weinstein
OL,19,Fand other big names in Hollywood.
